title: DDFP 464: Rooting for the L.A. Rams & Dear Ikey
itunes:title: DDFP 464: Rooting for the L.A. Rams & Dear Ikey
description:
Shek is joined by Chris Wesseling and Matt Franciscovich to discuss Karlos Williams' off-season weight gain, difficulties facing the Broncos and Panthers in 2016 and the ethics of rooting for the Los Angeles Rams. Also, Ike Taylor sits down with Shek to discuss the feeling of winning a championship. Plus, the guys compete in another surprise game show and the guys wrap with a chat about “Game of Thrones.”

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
